specific_issues.description: FY 2017 Appropriations for Departments of Labor, Health and Human Services, Education and related agencies: funding for DOL, OSHA, Wage and Hour Division, NLRB, NMB, policy riders and funding prohibitions regarding OSHA, DOL and NLRB. Appropriations bills and policy riders. Tribal Labor Sovereignty Act Rider; H.R. 511/ S. 248, Tribal Labor Sovereignty Act. Policy rider to prevent the NLRB from modifying its joint employer rule. Policy rider to prohibit implementation of the NLRB election rule. Policy rider to prevent the NLRB from applying its community of interest test (Specialty Health Care decision). Policy rider to prohibit the NLRB electronic voting. Provision to prohibit the DOL from implementing Fair Pay and Safe Workplace Executive ORder. Enforcement of minimum wage requirement for federal contractors. Policy rider to prohibit OSHA inspection "walk around" rule. Proposal to block OSHA silica standard. Proposal to block DOL fiduciary rule. Proposal to block DOL proposed overtime changes. FY 2017, Department of Transportation-HUD Appropriations provision regarding truck size and weight and meals and rest break requirements.
